{"id": 1210, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在“吃”这件事上认真到什么程度？", "description": "讲究起来，我妈都不认识我了。（题图来自：minicubby）", "record_count": 2955, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160908155009xRJupd7GUY2IzP5a.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-09T17:00:25Z", "options": [{"id": 114690, "content": "花了三个小时，地铁换公交来到燕郊，就因为有个人说要给我做螃蟹吃，西南山区来的，没吃过不会做，为了吃上一口现成的，也是拼了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751445}, {"id": 125442, "content": "拿个秤，秤好所有的分量，不能超过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781998}, {"id": 114691, "content": "早上7点起床吃大闸蟹", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753491}, {"id": 114692, "content": "做饭的步骤必须严格遵循，一点儿都不能有偏差！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650904}, {"id": 114948, "content": "饿了会发脾气", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738096}, {"id": 114693, "content": "要多不认真 有多不认真", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739093}, {"id": 114694, "content": "每一套菜都需要有辣椒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753493}, {"id": 114950, "content": "上午第一节下课和同桌讨论中午吃什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696513}, {"id": 114695, "content": "去一个城市，先看好美食推荐，然后列清单挨个吃遍。在广州玩，为吃一家双皮奶，专程地铁加步行两小时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753494}, {"id": 114696, "content": "必须认真拍，必须认真评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684225}, {"id": 114697, "content": "为了吃，丢了谈了9年的女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591982}, {"id": 114698, "content": "出门逛街朋友买衣服我买吃的，还有就是在我吃东西的时候千万不要", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327264}, {"id": 114699, "content": "愿意为了吃饭接受早上七点钟起床", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695521}, {"id": 114955, "content": "每天最令我头疼的就是：吃什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698825}, {"id": 119819, "content": "走在路上除了卖吃的的店 看不到别的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774544}, {"id": 114700, "content": "吃\n就是生命的全部。", "image": "img/option/option/20160910204921Y2bZyiIDTkcM3dmF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705681}, {"id": 114956, "content": "不合口味，直接吃不饱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682194}, {"id": 115212, "content": "曾经我妈想把我当猪喂 吃的越多越好 现在死活不让我吃 零用钱不给 煮饭定量 多吃一口粥 都会语重心长的对我说 娃儿啊 乖 别吃了 你不能再吃了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754367}, {"id": 114701, "content": "别人吃得正嗨，我指出了abcd种异味……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 114702, "content": "没有称心的食物感觉自己只是为了生存而完成任务\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687508}, {"id": 114958, "content": "吃就好好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754705}, {"id": 114703, "content": "旅游的目的都是为了满足胃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724960}, {"id": 114959, "content": "不出门的我为了小龙虾出门了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747073}, {"id": 118287, "content": "别人旅行是去买包，而我是买面包......(¯﹃¯)", "image": "img/option/option/20160922145716lBcA9pPVsdz21S7k.JPG", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699995}, {"id": 114704, "content": "泡面也要讲究水量和时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683525}, {"id": 114705, "content": "因为回国男朋友没有给买红烧肉，回国请吃饭居然请吃的是蔬菜而分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753543}, {"id": 114961, "content": "如果男朋友抢我的食物我会对爱情绝望", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682293}, {"id": 114706, "content": "吃得开心的时候会左右摇起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620645}, {"id": 114707, "content": "为了吃放弃减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733532}, {"id": 114708, "content": "为了吃放弃减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733532}, {"id": 114964, "content": "一个人的话吃什么都行，但是和朋友一起就大吃大喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754702}, {"id": 114453, "content": "初中的时候物理期末考为了吃早餐，迟到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114671}, {"id": 114709, "content": "为了吃放弃减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733532}, {"id": 114198, "content": "吃游，以吃为路线制定行程", "image": null, "praise_count": 563, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114454, "content": "一个人随便吃点儿，有什么好认真的", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262394}, {"id": 114710, "content": "每天都在问吃什么呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753562}, {"id": 114966, "content": "为了吃正宗的火锅，从南京飞重庆吃，只为一口满足感！！！??", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689580}, {"id": 117526, "content": "随便到没有底线！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564465}, {"id": 114199, "content": "自愿进行米其林式评测，上海最好吃牛肉面当属镇坪路敦煌驻沪办", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114455, "content": "吃。。。是我生命中另一种呼吸的方式?", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667933}, {"id": 114711, "content": "为了吃一间喜欢的餐厅。可以开8小时的车，再排队三个小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753564}, {"id": 114967, "content": "为了吃完一碗肉片，和团队相隔江的两岸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561711}, {"id": 116503, "content": "完全沉浸在食物里，甚至感觉不到发生了什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759858}, {"id": 114200, "content": "时间不要紧，“烧烤排行榜第一名”半夜等位一小时也没关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114456, "content": "环城觅食，环游觅食，不是在吃就是在去的路上", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213294}, {"id": 114712, "content": "一个城市好不好玩完全取决于有没有吃到好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753565}, {"id": 114201, "content": "大众点评上总是很认真地写评价，感觉在给每一道菜写传记", "image": null, "praise_count": 140, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 114457, "content": "对所有点外卖的人嗤之以鼻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116772}, {"id": 114713, "content": "去旅游先找遍特产食品和吃遍小吃街 ，然后再去看风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751146}, {"id": 114969, "content": "以时间计算，我不是在吃饭，就是在等待吃饭的漫长岁月里", "image": "img/option/option/201609112039042w0YDeQKy7PCbHOv", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91118}]}